Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure, 120 over 30;\Npulse, 92.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now remove the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have removed the bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The removal is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.63,0:00:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little early to be relieved;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,we must still reinforce the walls\Nof the damaged blood vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the proline ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure, 123 over 72;\Npulse, 33.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.54,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems the anesthesia is still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.76,0:02:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best to survive...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...Dr. Boyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like yours went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The surgery did...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Is that so...?\NThat's a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! You act as though\Nit's none of your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the very one\Nwho abandoned our team
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,just before surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...but, that child\Nwas brought in before the mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it matter, who was first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is, because you selfishly\Npulled out of our team,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,we were forced to try to fill\Nthe vacuum you created!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... Listen to me! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You upset the teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,By order of the Director,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.24,0:03:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I instructed you\Nto perform the surgery...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,on the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But you... You ignored me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.25,0:03:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but, Chief, at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The success of a surgery\Ndepends upon trust
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,among the entire staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you made a grand stand play!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already reported this\Nto the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.26,0:04:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He greatly regrets this incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,which has lowered\Nthe prestige of this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a minute!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.52,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At present, that child's blood pressure\Nis 114 over 32; pulse, 34.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,His vitals are very stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...\NThat's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... That operation...\NIt was wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mayor Roddecker, who collapsed\Nwhile on holiday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.55,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has passed away at the hospital.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Upon hearing this unexpected news,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}people have been arriving\Nat the Mayor's office{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}with bouquets of flowers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}many reminiscing on\Nthe life of the Mayor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A press conference has just been held\Nat Eisler Memorial Hospital{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}where the Mayor was taken.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The cause of\NMayor Roddecker's death{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was due to a cerebral infarction\Nstemming from{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a severe emphraxis\Nof the inner carotid artery{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We did everything we could for him,\Nbut it caused severe brain swelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,which resulted in\Nthis unfortunate outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As for naming a successor,\Na city official explained that{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}concrete steps will be taken{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-as soon as possible.{\i0}\N-I've got to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the case of the murder of\NMr. and Mrs. Liebert late last night...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Judging from the signs of\Na search in the rooms,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}police believe\Nthis may have been a robbery..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or perhaps the act of\Na political terrorist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}against this couple\Nwho had fled here from their country{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A two-pronged investigation\Nis under way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of this couple's twin children, the son,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.41,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}who received a gunshot wound\Nto the head{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}underwent successful surgery but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}has still to regain consciousness.\NHe is listed in critical condition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, for the weather...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The whole country is{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}-in for clear weather...{\i0}\N-That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what will happen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.26,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Reinhardt in ICU\Nis complaining that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,she just can't sleep..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we give her something\Nto help her sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh...in that case,\Ngive her one Halcyon tablet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...! He's been unfocused\Nall day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Becker...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you've had a trying time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the Director\Nhanded down his judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I warned you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you the hospital\Nis ruled by politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you played your cards right,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,your future would have been\Nsmooth sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.95,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...I guess this means you and I\Nare in the same boat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, don't be so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get a chance\Nto redeem your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go have some drinks.\NIt'll cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need to get a statement\Nfrom the girl twin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't discuss that with you now,\NDetective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is gone from her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl is always\Nslipping out of her room
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and wandering through the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eisler Memorial Hospital has\Nproven to be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the nation's leading medical facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That is first and foremost,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the result of our being blessed with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,such excellent personnel\Nsuch as you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sincerely grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.47,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.51,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,unfortunately, the Mayor died\Nhere in this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as always,\Nwe had done our utmost to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The public's evaluation of this hospital\Nhas not changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a round of applause\Nfor Dr. Boyer and Dr. Eisen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,who strived to the end\Nto save the Mayor's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at your paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you will continue to\Nwork on your research.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Director Heinemann!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I must apologize\Nfor my actions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now... What's done is done.\NDirector?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You did what you thought you should.\NLet's leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,let's have a word from\Nthe Head of Neurosurgery!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me... I'm being called up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.49,0:10:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the newly appointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer, please...\NPlease come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, what is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to remain at this hospital,\Nyou may do so,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but you'd better give up the idea of\Nrising any further as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be impossible for\Nsomeone with a flawed character
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,such as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll recognize your skill as a surgeon,\Nbut that is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You should also give up any ideas of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,presenting any papers\Nat future conferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, sir... Please listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you wish to move\Nto another hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of\Nwriting you a recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.36,0:10:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This means it's no use for you\Nto have any ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.07,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You may consider your path\Nto becoming
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the doctor you envisioned closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Surgery requires teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Only with the help of each\Nand every one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,can a life be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva, won't you talk to your father\Nfor me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I just operated on\Nan emergency case
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,in the order in which\Nhe was brought in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...your engagement ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.33,0:11:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.37,0:11:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Dr. Norden,\Ndon't you look elegant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As do you! You're more beautiful\Nthan ever tonight, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What a laugh, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,After coming across\NDirector Heinemann's paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to Germany,\Nand he made me what I am today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.96,0:12:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that paper\Nthat I was so impressed by
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,was probably written for him\Nby someone somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that he was using me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but I believed,\Nwhen I reached a certain position,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be able to work on research\Nof my choice to my heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are scholars, first and foremost.\NIsn't that right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not right! Saving people's lives\Nis what's most important to a doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, people's lives\Naren't created equal.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no distinction\Nbetween people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You say there's a flaw\Nin my character?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a doctor;\Nbut you're just money hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard... That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.05,0:14:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I have you to thank...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You opened my eyes, as a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You must do your best to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I threw everything away\Nin order to operate on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how far I went\Nin order to bring you back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know your name, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is Anna Liebert,\Nisn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I, Detective?\NIt's too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't anything be done, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she saw her parents\Nshot to death before her very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no physical wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but extreme trauma seems to have\Nbrought on amnesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please refrain from
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to get a statement from her\Nfor a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a difficult case, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The victim was\Nan East German diplomat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't solve this quickly,\Nthe BKA will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys always come
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and steal the thunder from\Nus state police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got the time to take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... What if we do this?\NWe let her see her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be relieved to see him\Nand her memory might return.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot agree on such a gamble–\None suggested by an amateur, at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Dr. Tenma\Nwill probably not permit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the doctor\Nin charge of her brother Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk... What the heck\Nam I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.48,0:16:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be in a daze.\NYou look awfully tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been so busy\Nwith emergency surgeries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been working you\Nto the bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,ever since you were\Ndemoted from Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind.\NIt actually makes me feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now... Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.70,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I've just been paged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.31,0:16:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so tired,\Nbut you still have work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The more diligent you are,\Nthe worse it'll be for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this, Director Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,See all the gifts\Nand letters of encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There are mountains of them\Nin his sister's room, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After losing their parents\Nthese two only have each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The mass media keeps reporting on\Ntheir heartbreaking plight,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and this is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as this hospital is concerned,\Nthey're nothing but an inconvenience;
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,what with no sign of anyone paying\Ntheir medical expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So their story is a pitiful one–\Nthat's just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.07,0:17:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That means this hospital is\Ngarnering attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason alone,\Nthese kids are valuable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we do this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give the media\Na photo of the siblings together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the media keeps asking\Nfor something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it. It'll be a picture\Nof the orphaned siblings
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,trying their best to live\Nwithin the warmhearted care
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,of our hospital's staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.61,0:17:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But the boy's doctor says\Nit is still too early
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to allow them to see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's on his case?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Dismiss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to give that man\Na position that gets so much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Dr. Tenma off the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:17:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a heartwarming gift\Nfrom the citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.07,0:18:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel, Mrs. Hankel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, I feel quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stitches will be removed soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so it won't be long\Nuntil you're released.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be able to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but as I said, you must rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.27,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Mrs. Hankel regular doses
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,of an anticonvulsant\Nand a hypotensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.12,0:18:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They let her see her brother.\NThen she gave a loud scream and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you bring them together?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her back to her room, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.07,0:19:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer, what is the meaning of this?\NWhy the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... We're going to give the media
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.28,0:19:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a picture of the emotional meeting\Nof the two children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.88,0:19:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who allowed you to do such a thing?\NI am the boy's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been dismissed\Nas Johan's doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As of today, he is my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided that it would be fine\Nto let them see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.90,0:19:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make those children fodder\Nfor the media!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it by order of the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it would be best for you\Nnot to fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who saved this boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a duty to protect him\Nuntil he is completely healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Ntake a look at the boy's reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.49,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as he saw his sister,\Nhe extended his hand and cried tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He regained consciousness\Nand showed a normal reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.00,0:20:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That means the surgery\Nwas a great success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job. Your work is done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back to where you belong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...\NDon't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what the Director says?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.06,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares what the Chief says?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all money and power hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I am not wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Father? Are you in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief...?\NAre you still in a meeting at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, are you asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.31,0:22:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard... He's better off dead...
